name: The Digital God - Stage Design - Render Version
description: Marcelo Alt, 2019. This piece was originally created as a stage design for New Vision Music Festival in Goiânia, Brazil. The concept idea is a Digital God that is always listening the music and beat frequency. It's build based in a alien tecnology and he can dialog directly with your soul. It was found in a cave of a far planet and there is no clue of who created it. | @vj_alt | www.artstation.com/vjalt |
